00:11:08,624 --> 00:11:09,862
No. I'm her attending, Maggie.

284
00:11:09,886 --> 00:11:10,886
I'm not her buddy.

285
00:11:13,498 --> 00:11:15,868
Mr. Acosta, I'm Dr. Tanaka-Reed.

286
00:11:15,892 --> 00:11:17,827
We're gonna take good
care of you, okay?

287
00:11:17,851 --> 00:11:19,263
Everyone watch the wires.

288
00:11:19,287 --> 00:11:21,985
On my count. One, two, three.

289
00:11:24,335 --> 00:11:25,791
I need to go home.
Emily is waiting.

290
00:11:25,815 --> 00:11:28,141
I need to go home.
- Patient's perseverating.

291
00:11:28,165 --> 00:11:29,360
Let's give two of Versed.
- Got it.

292
00:11:29,384 --> 00:11:30,970
Oh, no, wait a second.

293
00:11:30,994 --> 00:11:32,102
BP's soft.

294
00:11:32,126 --> 00:11:33,451
Yeah, but he's clearly agitated.

295
00:11:33,475 --> 00:11:34,844
How do you know the
change of mental status

296
