00:17:59,208 --> 00:18:00,881
Just got Mason's X-ray back.

464
00:18:00,905 --> 00:18:03,188
Mm, good.

465
00:18:03,212 --> 00:18:05,712
Greenstick fracture
of the left humerus.

466
00:18:05,736 --> 00:18:08,498
It need to be splinted, but
looks like it should heal

467
00:18:08,522 --> 00:18:10,021
just fine on its own, right?

468
00:18:10,045 --> 00:18:12,284
Correct.

469
00:18:12,308 --> 00:18:13,720
Okay, then.

470
00:18:13,744 --> 00:18:16,941
Why do you look like
the sky is falling?

471
00:18:16,965 --> 00:18:19,944
It's highly suspect to
see a humerus fracture

472
00:18:19,968 --> 00:18:21,491
